Class Polynomial

java.lang.Object
  Polynomial

public class Polynomial
extends java.lang.Object

Polynomial Program This program is designed to provide a basic framework for a polynomial in code, although it isn't designed to provide anything other than basic mathematical functions and the loading of these polynomials.

Author:
Scott Gardner

Function that returns a polynomial containing the monomials in a file, each monomial should be a coefficient and an exponent separated by a comma, and each monomial to a separate line.
